Title: Taken 3
Writer: Luc Besson, Robert Mark Kamen, Luc Besson (characters), Robert Mark Kamen (based on characters created by)
Actors: Liam Neeson, Forest Whitaker, Famke Janssen, Maggie Grace
Plot: Accused of a ruthless murder he never committed or witnessed, Bryan Mills goes on the run and brings out his particular set of skills to find the true killer and clear his name.
Production: EuropaCorp, M6 Films Production, Canal Plus
